definitions.definition: The process of computing the sum of an addition with one and the same number a specified number of times (i.e. 4 times 5 = [0 +] 5 + 5 + 5 + 5 = 20) or any other analogous binary operation that combines other mathematical objects.
The process of multiplying or increasing in number; increase .

main_definition: ( uncountable , arithmetic ) The process of computing the sum of an addition with one and the same number a specified number of times (i.e. 4 times 5 = [0 +] 5 + 5 + 5 + 5 = 20) or any other analogous binary operation that combines other mathematical objects.
secondary_definitions: ( countable , arithmetic ) A calculation involving multiplication.
The process of multiplying or increasing in number; increase .
